com.bigdata.gom.om

Interface IIDGenerator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IDGenerator

    public interface IIDGenerator
    The IIDGenerator interface is used to create default object URI ids for new objects. This can be exploited by various use cases where a unique id can be conveniently managed by the system.

    The interface allows applications to control the ID creation if required.

    Author:
    Martyn Cutcher

        Generate a globally unique URI.
        Parameters:
